{"tid":1463654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「癱瘓」同「唔癱瘓」有冇一個平衡點？","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:26.000Z","uid":151313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f5eda5f591a5e8fb4bd4a85061b44ca973824717","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"點解塞鐵會咁多人反對？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為一塞就完全搭唔到啊嗎！！</span><br />\n<br />\n但係機場，你唔係走落跑道，放無人機，都冇可能真正塞到。會唔會有一個方法唔係完全阻住人搭飛機，完全阻住空運服務，但係又同癱瘓好接近？<br />\n<br />\n例如淨係開放一個閘比人離境，令所有人都要排唯一一條隊，好慢好慢咁離境。<br />\n<br />\n又或者係喺機場島內慢駛，令到大塞車。<br />\n<br />\n以下開放比大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b39b24211d26702a2fbb41eba852a3fe880ad29","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee4c01ef12e3217a3a5ed42647daa3d9b816a86b","tid":1463654,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"認住呢幾間啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1463395/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1463395/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"45d5eb53f95f503e50381bf25cc33b9a9ee7b644","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a954c50c5f0530809dbaf03df502f56ab6cbb1a","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0847f052ba1ae06c60e71a53f4308b7108969b02","tid":1463654,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"攬炒!!!"},{"pid":"3dd8a00e499c6690c0dff30c8f5c3c2285b99120","tid":1463654,"uid":36761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"我地目標係對全世界做文宣,<br />\n人多自然癱瘓到,<br />\n就算唔夠人都或多或少造到影響<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">機場自己停=機場airline要賠錢<br />\n主動阻旅客=強烈反感, 仲點爭取國際支持?</span><br />\n如果100%癱瘓, 無服務=無旅客無職員<br />\n黑警到時可以落閘放狗, 瘋狂掃射<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">機場係持久戰! 唔可以自己玩爛個場</span><br />\n勇武休息 和理非接力全面升級<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;m not saying the protesters are playing with fire. I think the protesters want fire&rdquo;<br />\n香港人，我地有能力攬炒全球！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUgwqtg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUgwqtg.png&h=81aa5764&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9051aa78243c1efa4f6adf6330f3b4788f32e8b","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8727144884329ac7fd2328be27125818e75eec2b","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09ca0642a65cf0dff74a75544297d4ace39f9712","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f89087fd47fcdf384777865fb7f9ba29040d62c","tid":1463654,"uid":57005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:15.000Z","msg":"我認同留一條路俾佢地行，學另一個POST鬼佬講<br />\n佢地係支持我地，但而家搞到佢地有反感"},{"pid":"c9683e8b90e3b47ba8216d58fae44b3dcb774ecb","tid":1463654,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"每15分鐘放行一次？"},{"pid":"96da4cb3fd37704bea4e043161e56e014b556940","tid":1463654,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6344e6cb0bdb196c13019992341bc0851f92b50","tid":1463654,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"先唔好做主動blockade<br />\n靠人多盡量jam左佢先"},{"pid":"52deb9c92202c3f7eb426b747432c8d7002159fc","tid":1463654,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"好文一推"},{"pid":"dfeb93a9ba3cfa95a969cd7d04ee3f9087277593","tid":1463654,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"6fcec0d4239fb8d3cbe84fcd38a4890c366d0af4","tid":1463654,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"人多自然塞"},{"pid":"cea412eb7865097b58e6f36c5651c1b01fed3a08","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ce2580c113511acf5653fc07458ecdd79e623ed","tid":1463654,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec018cfe4dfff4e28de92ded5db58454f2546c6","tid":1463654,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51ffb321f45e7adde62db3941d28522ba82b0620","tid":1463654,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d74dadc413a0abd90eb2e339c696ff9d9758f1f","tid":1463654,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8.18!!! 荃葵青大遊行改左去 8.25! NOW OR NEVER</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"30e88563892f5aad6c8a8853a8c977bbb1a4d7ab","tid":1463654,"uid":273637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"一人一架無人機有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"8ed66129b8d3904440b973a438684ac9b7221cd8","tid":1463654,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X74U7Rj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F